## Effects of mutations to rabies G on escape from antibody RVC20

Pseudovirus deep mutational scanning of how mutations to rabies G affect
neutralization by antibody RVC20 shown on pH domain (6tou).


Structure shown is from PDB 6tou.

Study by Arjun Aditham and Jesse Bloom (2024).
See [https://github.com/dms-vep/RABV_Pasteur_G_DMS](https://github.com/dms-vep/RABV_Pasteur_G_DMS) for code.
